                              role="owner" type="person">Elín Hákonardóttir</name> í Vatnsfirði and <name key="HelMag001"
                                 role="owner" type="person">Helga
                              Magnúsdóttir</name>, son of Björnsson the lawman. Árni mentions Helga having received the manuscript
